1
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:20,560
Honey

2
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:22,359
I'll be away on business for three days

3
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,079
Come give me some love

4
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,760
Get off

5
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:27,079
The baby's right next to us

6
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,000
Can't you see that?

7
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:30,079
She's already fast asleep

8
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:32,319
We'll be sneaky about it

9
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:38,840
Su Yuanyuan

10
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:40,319
keeps pestering Bai Li

11
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,920
to get He Junjie to write a letter of forgiveness

12
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,079
Tell me

13
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,560
Will she do something drastic?

14
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,879
That's really hard to say

15
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:50,319
If it were you,

16
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,239
would you?

17
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:53,280
Why are you comparing me to her?

18
00:01:53,519 --> 00:01:55,000
Are you asking for it?

19
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:57,879
Honey

20
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:00,079
During these three days I'm away,

21
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:02,680
take the baby and stay at your mom's

22
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,959
You're worried?

23
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,920
I'm just afraid

24
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,759
that during the three days I'm gone,

25
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,719
the two of you might be in danger

26
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:18,879
Okay?

27
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:19,479
Mm

28
00:03:38,639 --> 00:03:39,759
How are you feeling today?

29
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,000
Pretty good.

30
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,199
Doctor,

31
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,400
can I be discharged?

32
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,479
You're recovering well,

33
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:49,719
but for a discharge,

34
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,960
we need to observe you for two more days.

35
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,400
I can come back for check-ups on my own.

36
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,360
Doctor,

37
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,240
I want to be discharged today.

38
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:55,879
I don't want to stay here

39
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:56,759
for even a second longer.

40
00:03:57,479 --> 00:03:58,319
I understand

41
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,120
how you feel.

42
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:00,280
But today,

43
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,039
you definitely can't be discharged.

44
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,560
Then tomorrow.

45
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,520
I'm leaving first thing tomorrow morning.

46
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,479
Look how happy you are.

47
00:04:08,879 --> 00:04:10,360
Are you rushing out to rob a bank?

48
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:11,919
Yifan is on a business trip.

49
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:13,000
I need to get back to work.

50
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:15,479
You still need the doctor's approval.

51
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,600
The doctor has already agreed.

52
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,240
I'll go tell Li Yao in a bit.

53
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,720
Why didn't you mention going home

54
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,839
to see our son first?

55
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:22,600
You're right.

56
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:24,839
I haven't seen our son in days.

57
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:25,879
How about this:

58
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,600
I'll pick him up from school with you later.

59
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,319
Let's surprise him.

60
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:29,639
Mm, that's more like it.

61
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:40,160
Nurse,

62
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,519
where's the patient from this bed?

63
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:44,560
Two officers came this morning

64
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,480
and took him away.

65
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:56,800
Li Yao isn't a bad person at heart.

66
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:58,439
He's taken so many wrong turns.

67
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:01,079
I hope he gets a lenient sentence.

68
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:08,959
Han, don't think you're safe just because I'm wanted!

69
00:05:08,959 --> 00:05:12,000
Are you trying to kick me when I'm down?

70
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,040
I gave you so much money before.

71
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,360
Now you have to pay me back every single cent.

72
00:05:18,079 --> 00:05:19,720
Where would I get that much money now?

73
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,920
Just leave, and don't look for me again.

74
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,360
The police are after you.

75
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,279
You...

76
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,279
You...

77
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:27,720
You can ask your wife.

78
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,199
Or your mistresses.

79
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:30,639
Even your Aunt is richer than me.

80
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,680
If I don't see the money tomorrow,

81
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,600
your whole family will pay for it.

82
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,040
Three days.

83
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,399
Give me three days

84
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:40,759
to raise the money, alright?

85
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,519
Are you ever going to stop?

86
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,439
Just try taking a single cent from this house!

87
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,160
All these years, you haven't earned a dime.

88
00:05:46,879 --> 00:05:47,720
Look at Xiao Yifan.

89
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:48,800
He's already

90
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,800
a General Manager.

91
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:51,680
You're still just an Assistant.

92
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:52,839
Useless!

93
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:54,120
What's the point of marrying you?

94
00:05:55,639 --> 00:05:56,040
I...

95
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,800
Don't ever mention Xiao Yifan to me again.

96
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,079
Did you tell Chairman Zheng I'm out of the hospital?

97
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,199
Don't worry.

98
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:15,360
I've already told him.

99
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:17,560
Good.

100
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,439
Then when Yifan gets back from his trip,

101
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:20,639
we'll give him a surprise.

102
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,480
Sounds good.

103
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,120
I'll head back to the office first.

104
00:06:23,639 --> 00:06:23,959
Okay.

105
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,240
Let's go, son.

106
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,399
Off we go, son.

107
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:28,319
Can you manage?

108
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:28,959
Come on.

109
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,000
You just got out of the hospital.

110
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,519
It's fine.

111
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:40,800
Enough.

112
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,560
I'll do it myself.

113
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,079
Go get the work plan.

114
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:51,959
Ah.

115
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,519
It's so good to be back at work.

116
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,199
I love working.

117
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,680
Work makes me happy.

118
00:06:58,759 --> 00:07:00,160
Brother, I'm back.

119
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,279
Hurry back too.

120
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,600
How do you have the nerve to come see me?

121
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,519
President He,

122
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,319
we've been friends for so many years,

123
00:07:15,319 --> 00:07:16,560
and we've always gotten along.

124
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:18,560
You could forgive Li Yao,

125
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,160
so why can't you forgive Fang Bing?

126
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,519
Su Yuanyuan,

127
00:07:22,199 --> 00:07:23,600
Fang Bing kidnapped my child.

128
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,279
How could I possibly forgive him?

129
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,279
I went to see Yifan.

130
00:07:30,279 --> 00:07:31,879
Why isn't he in his office?

131
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,160
Listen, Su Yuanyuan,

132
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,199
Are you out of your mind?

133
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:36,959
With Fang Bing on the run,

134
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:38,759
you think the police aren't tracking you?

135
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,879
Every move you make

136
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:42,480
is under police surveillance.

137
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:44,519
No way.

138
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,360
Do you know how many years

139
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,839
your husband could get for his crimes?

140
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:49,240
Instead of wasting time looking for me,

141
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,360
you'd better hurry up

142
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,160
and find a good lawyer.

143
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,160
Xiao Yifan!

144
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:13,000
Fang Bing.

145
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,639
Why haven't you run yet?

146
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:17,560
We were equals as Party A and Party B.

147
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:20,519
You schemed against my Aunt to take Plot 6,

148
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:23,000
then tricked my wife into buying the restricted-sale property.

149
00:08:23,079 --> 00:08:24,160
Today, nobody's leaving alive.

150
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,120
Kill him.

151
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,159
Awesome!

152
00:09:26,039 --> 00:09:27,879
Dad, did you get mugged?

153
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,080
What happened?

154
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:33,120
Who hit you?

155
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:34,600
I'm fine.

156
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:35,759
I brought you guys gifts.

157
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:37,120
They're in the suitcase.

158
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:39,240
Dad, did you get into a fight

159
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,279
to protect the gifts?

160
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:44,919
Come here.

161
00:09:46,039 --> 00:09:46,960
Hurry up and tell us!

162
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,720
Fang Bing.

163
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,960
He tried to ambush me in the parking garage.

164
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:52,039
So I beat him up.

165
00:09:52,399 --> 00:09:52,799
What?

166
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,279
Did you call the police?

167
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,200
Was Fang Bing caught?

168
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:57,799
You know your husband, don't you?

169
00:09:58,399 --> 00:09:59,320
He definitely took him

170
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,360
to the police station himself.

171
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,559
Did you miss Daddy?

172
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,279
Yes!

173
00:10:17,159 --> 00:10:18,440
Su Yuanyuan, what are you doing here?

174
00:10:22,759 --> 00:10:23,440
Xiao Yifan.
